Package commonMethods

Class ProjectConfigData

java.lang.Object
commonMethods.ProjectConfigData
public class ProjectConfigData
extends java.lang.Object
ProjectConfigData class implements to read data from xml file by calling getDataFromXml method, and getters to access class fields where is stored data from xml file
